/*
-- You can use different solutions to find the annual oil consumption for example: --
 1. To get the oil consumption for each country or region for a specific year (e.g., 2012)
 2. To get the oil consumption for each country or region for multiple years (e.g., from 2010 to 2020)
 3. To get the oil consumption for a specific country or region (e.g., "Asia") for all years
*/


Solution 1.

SELECT 
    countries_continent, 
    year_2012
FROM
    oil_consumption;

